      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Way of the Pukei",
        "Client": "Utsushi Fangirl",
        "Description": "Master Utsushi does those monster\r\nimpressions, right? Maybe if I, like,\r\nlearned one, we\u0027d have something in\r\ncommon. I bet I could do Pukei-Pukei.\r\nSeems easy. I\u0027m already pretty good\r\nat sticking out my tongue. If you hunt\r\none for me, I can watch and take notes!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Pukei-Pukei",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "La voie du Pukei",
        "Client": "Fan d\u0027Utsushi",
        "Description": "Ma\u00EEtre Utsushi fait bien des\r\nimitations de monstres ? Si je m\u0027y\r\nmets, on aurait un truc en commun...\r\nJe peux peut-\u00EAtre imiter un\r\nPukei-Pukei ? Je sais y faire avec\r\nma langue. Je pourrais prendre des\r\nnotes si tu vas en chasser un !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Pukei-Pukei",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Proprio come un Pukei",
        "Client": "Ammiratrice di Utsushi",
        "Description": "Il maestro Utsushi imita i\r\nmostri, vero? Se imparassi\r\nanch\u0027io, avremmo qualcosa in\r\ncomune. Sai, potrei imitare un\r\nPukei-Pukei. Sembra facile e\r\nso fare la linguaccia. Potrei\r\nstudiare se ne cacciassi uno.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Pukei-Pukei",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Der Weg des Pukei",
        "Client": "Utsushi-Verehrerin",
        "Description": "Meister Utsushi imitiert doch Monster,\r\noder? Wenn ich auch eins nachahmen\r\nk\u00F6nnte, h\u00E4tten wir was gemeinsam.\r\nPukei-Pukei krieg ich sicher hin. Ich\r\nkann schon ziemlich gut meine Zunge\r\nrausstrecken. Wenn du einen f\u00FCr mich\r\njagst, seh ich zu und mach Notizen!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Pukei-Pukei.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Intensa observaci\u00F3n Pukei",
        "Client": "Admiradora de Utsushi",
        "Description": "Necesito una excusa para\r\nhablar con el maestro Utsushi,\r\npero no soy cazadora. Debo\r\nrecurrir a las imitaciones de\r\nmonstruos. \u00BFPodr\u00EDas cazar un\r\nPukei-Pukei mientras miro para\r\nque aprenda a imitarlos?",
        "Target": "Caza un Pukei-Pukei",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041F\u0443\u0442\u044C \u041F\u043E\u043A\u0438",
        "Client": "\u0424\u0430\u043D\u0430\u0442\u043A\u0430 \u0423\u0446\u0443\u0441\u0438",
        "Description": "\u041C\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0435\u0440 \u0423\u0446\u0443\u0441\u0438 \u0443\u043C\u0435\u0435\u0442 \u0438\u0437\u043E\u0431\u0440\u0430\u0436\u0430\u0442\u044C\r\n\u043C\u043E\u043D\u0441\u0442\u0440\u043E\u0432. \u041C\u043E\u0436\u0435\u0442, \u043D\u0430\u0443\u0447\u0438\u0441\u044C \u044F \u0442\u0430\u043A\r\n\u0434\u0435\u043B\u0430\u0442\u044C, \u0443 \u043D\u0430\u0441 \u0431\u044B\u043B\u043E \u0431\u044B \u0447\u0442\u043E-\u0442\u043E\r\n\u043E\u0431\u0449\u0435\u0435. \u0427\u0442\u043E \u0435\u0441\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0437\u043E\u0431\u0440\u0430\u0437\u0438\u0442\u044C\r\n\u041F\u043E\u043A\u0438? \u042F\u0437\u044B\u043A \u044F \u0432\u044B\u0441\u043E\u0432\u044B\u0432\u0430\u044E\r\n\u043E\u0442\u043B\u0438\u0447\u043D\u043E. \u041F\u043E\u0439\u043C\u0430\u0439 \u0434\u043B\u044F \u043C\u0435\u043D\u044F \u041F\u043E\u043A\u0438,\r\n\u044F \u0431\u0443\u0434\u0443 \u0437\u0430 \u043D\u0438\u043C \u043D\u0430\u0431\u043B\u044E\u0434\u0430\u0442\u044C!",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u041F\u043E\u043A\u0438-\u041F\u043E\u043A\u0438",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POL",
        "Name": "Droga Pukei",
        "Client": "Fanka Utsushiego",
        "Description": "Mistrz Utsushi na\u015Bladuje potwory\r\n\u2013 mo\u017Ce je\u015Bli nauczy\u0142abym si\u0119\r\nudawa\u0107 jednego, co\u015B by nas\r\n\u0142\u0105czy\u0142o. Chyba da\u0142abym sobie rad\u0119\r\nz Pukei-Pukei. Jestem niez\u0142a\r\nw wyci\u0105ganiu j\u0119zyka. Upolujesz\r\ndla mnie jednego do nauki?",
        "Target": "Upoluj Pukei-Pukei",
        "Fail": "Nagroda = 0 lub koniec czasu"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POR",
        "Name": "Caminho do Pukei",
        "Client": "F\u00E3 do Utsushi",
        "Description": "O Utsushi \u00E9 bom em imitar monstros, n\u00E9?\r\nTalvez, se eu aprendesse uma imita\u00E7\u00E3o,\r\nter\u00EDamos algo em comum. Aposto que eu\r\nconsigo imitar um Pukei-Pukei. Parece\r\nf\u00E1cil. J\u00E1 sou muito boa em mostrar a\r\nl\u00EDngua. Se voc\u00EA ca\u00E7ar um pra mim,\r\nposso observar e tomar notas!",
